Index.php => render main template

Index.html.twig => HTML + JS (master)

USER => CLIC BUTTON HTML => call JS(master function)

Master.js => CALL => Ajax func JS

  - JS getConnection() => PHP connection.php (script connection API)
    [ http://localhost/V2/Ajax/connection.php ]

  - PHP connection.php => reponse OK|!OK + session_id (API for Call) => JS getConnection()

  - JS getConnection => JS getStatus()
    [ http://localhost/V2/Ajax/getStatus.php?player=channe&session=AE ]
        - player = "test"
        - session = "forced to (GET CONNECTION)"

  - JS getStatus => PHP getStatus()
  - PHP getStatus => Match ID + status + statusString => JS getStatus()
  - JS getStatus() => JS createMatch
    - JS createMatch => PHP createMatch() => BDD createMatch()
        [ http://localhost/V2/Ajax/createMatch.php?matchid=234226163 ]
            - matchid = 243226163
    - JS getPlayer => PHP getPlayers.php =>



  - JS getStatus()